        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "When she grew up, she was betrothed to a prince who lived a great way off; and as the time drew near for her to be married, she got ready to set off on her journey to his country.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
