        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "So when the bride had drunk, and would have got upon Falada again, the maid said, \"I shall ride upon Falada and you may have my horse instead;\" so she was forced to give up her horse, and soon afterwards to take off her royal clothes, and put on her maid's shabby ones.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110517_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110517/7886_110517_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "At last, as they drew near the end of the journey, this treacherous servant threatened to kill her mistress if she ever told anyone what had happened.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110517_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110517/7886_110517_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "\"I brought her with me for the sake of her company on the road,\" said she.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "But this queen died; and the king soon married another wife, who was very beautiful, but so proud that she could not bear to think that any one could surpass her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "\"Tell me, glass, tell me true! Of all the ladies in the land. Who is fairest?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
