        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "Tell me who?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "And the glass answered, \"Thou, Queen, art fairest in the land.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "Then the glass one day answered the queen, when she went to consult it as usual:",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "\"Thou, Queen, may'st fair and beauteous be, But Snow White is lovelier far than thee!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000007_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000007_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "In the evening she came to a little cottage, and went in there to rest herself, for her weary feet would carry her no further.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000007_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000007_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "They lighted up their seven lamps, and saw directly that all was not right.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000007_000010",
