        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "The sixth, \"Who has been cutting with my knife?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000007_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000007_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "The seventh, \"Who has been drinking my wine?\" Then the first looked round and said.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "In the morning Snow White told them all her story; and they pitied her, and said if she would keep all things in order, and cook and wash, and knit and spin for them, she might stay where she was, and they would take good care of her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "Then the queen was very much alarmed; for she knew that the glass always spoke the truth, and was sure that the servant had betrayed her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "Then she knocked at the door, and cried, \"Fine wares to sell!\" Snow White looked out of the window, and cried, \"Good day, good woman; what have you to sell?\" \"Good wares, fine wares,\" said she; \"laces and bobbins of all colours.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "\"I will let the old lady in; she seems to be a very good sort of a body,\" thought Snow White; so she ran down, and unbolted the door.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110518_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110518/7886_110518_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "\"Bless me!\" said the woman, \"how badly your stays are laced.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110519_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7886/110519/7886_110519_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "\"Fine clothes,\" said the first: \"Pearls and diamonds,\" said the second.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7886_110519_000000_000002",
