        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "\"Now, child,\" said he to his own daughter, \"what will you have?\" \"The first sprig, dear father, that rubs against your hat on your way home,\" said she.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
