        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "Then he waited till her father came home, and told him that the unknown maiden who had been at the feast had hidden herself in the pigeon house.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
