        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7886",
        "content": "Then the mother gave her a knife, and said, \"Never mind, cut it off; when you are queen you will not care about toes, you will not want to go on foot.\" So the silly girl cut her great toe off, and squeezed the shoe on, and went to the king's son.",
